extends ../layouts/default

block head
    meta(property="og:title" content="Register now for the SFL Ultimate Beach Series!")
    meta(property="og:url" content="https://www.sflultimate.com/register")
    meta(property="og:description" content="Sign up for the upcoming three beach hatters on Sat. Jan. 11th & Sat. February 1st")
    meta(property="og:image" content="https://www.sflultimate.com/images/beach-ultimate-series-logo.jpg")
    script(src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js?render=6Ld6rNQUAAAAAAthlbLL1eCF9NGKfP8-mQOHu89w")
block content

    .container.register: .row: .col-md-12

        if err
            br
            .alert.alert-danger
                strong Error:
                span=err
        br
        br
        h1=league.title + " Sign Up" 

        h3 Description
        p This fall we'll be back at Amelia Earhart Park, nearby where Le Jeune Road meets State Road 924.
        iframe(src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d14358.205887616712!2d-80.2784486!3d25.8842357!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x5fd60d3c7189a581!2sAmelia+Earhart+Park!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1475028057840" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen)

        p Regular season games will be <strong>Wednesday evenings at 8pm, starting October 6th</strong>. 
        p We're planning on 8 weeks of play on Wednesdays, skipping the Wednesday of Thanksgiving week and ending on Wednesday, December 1st. <strong>Finals are planned for December 12th, and will be</strong> at Amelia Earhart Park.

        p Registration is open <strong>as of September 28th and ends October 3rd</strong> and the costs are:
        ul
            li $30 for students
            li $50 for everyone else
        p The fee that we all pay for are for the access to the lit fields during regular season and playoffs as well as a basic insurance.
        
        .alert.alert-info Late registration (at a $65 fee for everyone, as space permits) will continue until after the first week of play.

        hr

        h3 Registration

        form#registration(method="post" action="register" autocomplete="off")

            .row
                .col-md-6
                    .form-group
                        label(for='first_name') First Name
                        input#first_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='first_name' placeholder='' required)
                .col-md-6
                    .form-group
                        label(for='last_name') Last Name
                        input#last_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='last_name' placeholder='' required)

            .form-group
                label(for='email') Email Address
                input#email.input-lg.form-control(type='email' name='email' placeholder='' required)
                p.help-block We send updates and league information through the email you provide here

            .form-group
                label(for="gender") Gender
                select#gender.input-lg.form-control(name="gender")
                    option(value='Female') Female
                    option(value='Male') Male
                p.help-block We use this information to draft teams that have even gender distributions
            
            .form-group
                label(for="skill_level") Skill Level
                    select#skill_level.input-lg.form-control(name="skill_level")
                        option(value='1') 1 - Absolute Beginner
                        option(value='2') 2 - Hey wait, what's a flick?
                        option(value='3') 3 - Working on throws, basic knowledge of game
                        option(value='4') 4 - Pickup player, okay throws
                        option(value='5') 5 - Decent backhand & forehand. Little to no club experience
                        option(value='6') 6 - Fairly solid backhand & forehand. Some club experience
                        option(value='7') 7 - Tourney experience. Several years of club
                        option(value='8') 8 - Club level, solid all around, not prone to errors
                        option(value='9') 9 - Rock star. spot on throws, awesome D
                p.help-block Please express this accurately as it helps captains balance skill-level across teams

            .form-group
                label(for='partner_name') Partner Name
                input#partner_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='partner_name' placeholder='')
                p.help-block Type the name of the person you would like to partner with


            .form-group
                label Comments
                textarea(name="comments").form-control
                p.help-block Type here any additional comments you may have
            
            .form-group
                label(for="captain_preference") Would you like to be a captain?
                select#captain_preference.input-lg.form-control(name="captain_preference")
                    option(value='No') No
                    option(value='Yes') Yes
            
            p.help-block Captains can draft their teams and are responsible for communicating benefits.

            h3 Waiver
            .checkbox
                label
                    input(type='checkbox', name='terms_conditions' required)
                    | I agree to SFLUltimate's <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#waiver">terms & conditions</a>.
                
            h3 COVID-19
            .checkbox
                label
                    input(type='checkbox', name='covid_19_no_risk' required)
                    | If I have tested positive for COVID-19, am waiting for COVID-19 test results, or am showing COVID-19 symptoms, or had close contact with a person who has tested positive for or who has symptoms of COVID-19, <strong>I will not attend any games until I have received a negative COVID-19 test</strong>.


            h3 Payment Information
            input(id="recaptcha" name='recaptcha_token' type='hidden')
            
            .form-group
                label(for="registration_level") Registration Level
                    select#registration_level.input-lg.form-control(name="registration_level")
                        option(value='adult') Adult - $50
                        option(value='student') Student - $30

            #payment-form
            .text-center
                button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-primary(type='submit' id='submit-button') Submit

